===Intransitive verb===
{{en-verb|wobbl|ing}}

# To [[move]] with an [[uneven]] or [[rock]]ing [[motion]], or [[unsteadily]] [[to and fro]].
#:''The Earth '''wobbles''' slowly on its axis as it rotates.''
#:''The jelly '''wobbled''' on the plate.''
# To [[tremble]] or [[quaver]].
#:''The soprano's voice '''wobbled''' alarmingly.''
# To [[vacillate]] in one's [[opinion]]s.
#:''I'm '''wobbling''' between the Liberals and the Greens.''

====Synonyms====
*(''move with an uneven or rocking motion''): [[judder]], [[shudder]], [[tremble]]
*(''quaver''): [[quaver]], [[tremble]]
*(''vacillate''): [[vacillate]], [[waver]]

